00:53:34,096 --> 00:53:52,422
very official looking thing you know here's the invoice you're looking for or what have you if she's doing 100 things in a day like she usually is maybe it gets through when she clicks on the pdf or what have you that's what they're banking on it's this mass mailing type of thing that goes on but what i've seen really the

